{
  "stem": "27507.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it was border between the Soviet Union and the German Generalgouvernement, what was the part of Poland occupied by Germans, what was called Generalgouvernement.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went to-- so after that, after we were freed, we went back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we found ourselves in Warsaw in April, 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Warsaw, we went back-- we moved back into our apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The apartment was not exactly what it was before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because for the start, we were not the only people living in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was as well a family of my mother, some family which we didn't know-- which I didn't know before the war, her uncle and cousins and-- and cousins and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some other family members.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they lived-- they moved-- they had to leave Lodzh.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure-- which is Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure if they had to leave or if they left Lodz out of their own will.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, they found themselves in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And indeed, they spend the rest of the war in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were in our apartment as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "End of Tape 2.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Goodness gracious.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
